description:
Song changes out the wazoo:

- Fixed all rhythm guitar parts. While the "Clean" guitar track isn't really accurate, it provides an adequate backing for the other tracks.
- Added all guitar harmonies.
- Fixed timing on just about everything. While some places could be a little more accurate, it is close enough to the original so as to not be jarring.
- Most importantly, corrected all wrong notes, added missing notes, and made it closer to how Marty plays it in many areas for those who care. Where I haven't given a part that treatment, again, I made sure the notes were at least correct.
title: Whiteworm
